Date: Tue, 12 Apr 2011 20:25:37 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 466/628] Xilinx: PS USB OTG Controller Driver

git://github.com/Xilinx/linux-xlnx.git xilinx-v14.7
commit 6845316fd648ba5e3fa65f557acbdd3a2706e09d

Added new driver files for PS USB OTG Controller.
This driver is same as intel langwell driver(langwell_otg.c)
with few minor modifications to support Xilinx PS USB controller.

Signed-off-by: Naveen Mamindlapalli <naveenm@xilinx.com>
Signed-off-by: Liming Wang <liming.wang@windriver.com>
---
 include/linux/usb/xilinx_usbps_otg.h |  212 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 1 files changed, 212 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)
 create mode 100644 include/linux/usb/xilinx_usbps_otg.h

diff --git a/include/linux/usb/xilinx_usbps_otg.h b/include/linux/usb/xilinx_usbps_otg.h
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..fdb3ec6
--- /dev/null
+++ b/include/linux/usb/xilinx_usbps_otg.h
@@ -0,0 +1,212 @@
